    <item>
      <title>法国财政部长暗示选举后未来将有所不同</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/france-s-finance-chief-hints-at-different-future-after-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国财政部长布鲁诺·勒梅尔表示，提前举行的立法选举使法国对下届政府陷入政治不确定性，因此他可能不会留任。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/france-s-finance-chief-hints-at-different-future-after-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 10:28:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>民意调查显示，工党在宣言日遥遥领先</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/bloomberg-uk-poll-of-polls-labour-has-big-lead-on-manifesto-day</link>
      <description><![CDATA[工党定于周四公布其选举承诺宣言，基尔·斯塔默领导的反对党在全国民意调查中遥遥领先，而且在竞选活动进行到一半时，这种领先优势没有丝毫减弱的迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/bloomberg-uk-poll-of-polls-labour-has-big-lead-on-manifesto-day</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
